This version of SpecProbe finishes all the work required to finalize support for FreeBSD and to resturucture parts of SpecProbe, while adding new features.

### Changes

This release contains a variety of changes, including, but not limited to:

- `[+]` Added removable hard drive support
- `[+]` Added error messages for loading libraries
- `[+]` Added L1, L2, and L3 support for FreeBSD and macOS (x64)
- `[+]` Added new ARM implementers
- `[+]` Added more PCI IDs
- `[*]` Merged SpecProbe.Native and SpecProbe.Loader to one library
- `[*]` Restructured parts of code
- `[*]` General improvements and bug fixes

Review the commit history if you want to get a deep insight about the changes.

### Feedback?

If you have issues with this version, report to us by [making a new issue ticket](https://github.com/Aptivi/SpecProbe/issues/new).

